local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["phenomenon"]={"phenomenon","[fɪ'nɒmɪnən]","[fə'nɑmɪnən]","n.现象",'n.现象,非凡的人或事物','A child who could read at the age of one would indeed be a phenomenon.','一个一岁的孩子能阅读，会被认为是个神童。','But their so-called prosperity is only a temporary phenomenon.','但他们所谓的繁荣只是一个暂时的现象。'}
